OL,3,CMan appears in court in connection to
OL,4,Cmurder of Danny McClean
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court in Belfast
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of Danny
OL,8,FMcClean, 54, who was shot and killed
OL,9,Fas he sat in a car parked in the
OL,10,Fdriveway of a property on Cliftonville
OL,11,FRoad in February 2021.
OL,13,FHugh Black, 50, of Rosehead, Belfast,
OL,14,Fappeared at the city's magistrates'
OL,15,Fcourt on Thursday.
OL,17,FHe has also been charged with the
OL,18,Fattempted murder of Sean O'Reilly
OL,19,Fearlier this year, as well as three
OL,20,Fcharges of possessing firearms with
OL,21,Fthe intent to endanger life.
