OL,3,CMan appears in court in connection to
OL,4,Cmurder of Danny McClean
OL,6,FMr O'Reilly, 49, was shot twice while
OL,7,Fhe was sitting in his taxi in the Bell
OL,8,FSteel Manor area of Belfast on
OL,9,FFebruary 23 this year. He survived the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FBlack appeared in the court following
OL,13,Fa technical issue with the video link.
OL,15,FHe said he understood the charges when
OL,16,Fthey were put to him.
OL,18,FA detective chief inspector said he
OL,19,Fcould connect Black to the offences.
