OL,4,Cmurder of Danny McClean
OL,6,FThe officer told the court that the
OL,7,Fpolice did not believe Black was one
OL,8,Fof the two gunmen involved in the
OL,9,Fshooting of Mr O'Reilly, but that he
OL,10,Fhad acted as a "lookout" and was
OL,11,F"crucial" to the plan.
OL,13,FThe detective also said that two guns
OL,14,Fand a jacket were found in a nearby
OL,15,Fhedge following the shooting of Mr
OL,16,FO'Reilly. One of them had its barrel
OL,17,Fdetached and was faulty.
