OL,6,FThe court heard Black denied all the
OL,7,Foffences in a prepared statement to
OL,8,Fpolice after two days of questioning.
OL,10,FDistrict Judge Anne Marshall said she
OL,11,Fwas satisfied Black could be connected
OL,12,Fto the charges and remanded him in
OL,13,Fcustody ahead of a bail hearing on
OL,14,FMonday.
